📝 Quiz Application

A simple Quiz Web Application built using Django.
Users can attempt quizzes and view results through a clean web interface.

🚀 Features

Create and manage quizzes
Attempt quiz questions
View results
Admin panel for managing questions

🛠️ Technologies Used

Python
Django
SQLite (Default Database)

📂 Project Structure
quiz/
│── manage.py
│── db.sqlite3
│── quiz/        (Project settings)
│── home/        (App)

▶️ How to Run
1️⃣ Navigate to project folder (where manage.py exists)
cd quiz

2️⃣ Install Django (if not installed)
pip install django

3️⃣ Run migrations
python manage.py migrate

4️⃣ Start server
python manage.py runserver

Open in browser:
http://127.0.0.1:8000/
